snippet.title: v7.2 The Wings to Mars Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v7.2 The Wings to Mars coming soon! New S-rank battlesuit Fenghuang of Vicissitude debuts!

Featured event Wild Phoenix Chase, new event The Star Which the Moon Gazes Upon and more events to be released! Stay tuned!

Voice Artist:
Fu Hua: Minami Takayama
